channel.title: Searching for partner
channel.description:
Hi all
Im searching for someone who wants to start a server with me. [317] like Delta or Allstar. We will start from scratch. I am looking for a passionate person who knows something about programming. I don`t have experience with an automatically donation system and webclients, so if you know anything about this would definitely be an advantage.
I have experience in:
[ul][li]Java[/li] [li]Visual Basic[/li] [li]C#[/li] [li]HTML[/li] [li]CSS[/li] [li]Photoshop[/li] [li]Assembler[/li] [li]PHP[/li][/ul]
Green = Good, Orange = Average, Red = little experience
You can contact me by sending a private message, with some information about yourself and some motivation.
Greetz Vincent
